        <item>
            <title>香港的士车队推 6 座电动的士，用 App 预约 + 预先电子付款 + 全车摄录系统</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/13/syncab-6-seat-taxi-availabe-today/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=syncab-6-seat-taxi-availabe-today</link>
